      </a>
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_E5B26E70-5D45-0136-0E2B-06467EE270FA" class="text-block-content">
    <p><a href="/t5/Instructor-Guide/How-do-I-create-a-quiz-using-New-Quizzes/ta-p/1173" target="_blank">Instructors can use New Quizzes</a> to build quizzes with several item types that measure student competency in a variety of subjects. Quizzes can be modified <a href="/t5/Instructor-Guide/How-do-I-manage-settings-for-a-quiz-in-New-Quizzes/ta-p/581" target="_blank">using various quiz settings</a> and aligned to outcomes at the quiz or question level.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>
 
