  <div id="text-content_E5B2F1B0-5D45-0136-0E31-06467EE270FA" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Instructors can <a href="/t5/Instructor-Guide/How-do-I-use-the-Moderation-page-in-New-Quizzes/ta-p/616" target="_blank">moderate student attempts and review students' answers</a>.</p>
  </div>
