    <p>Students can <a href="/t5/Student-Guide/How-do-I-view-my-quiz-results-as-a-student-in-New-Quizzes/ta-p/289" target="_blank">view their results from New Quizzes quizzes</a>. Quiz results include overall and individual questions scores. They may also include instructor feedback.</p>
